              "file": "knowledge/adr/2026-06-01-2300-review-fixer-self-resolve-scope-files.md",
              "line": 27,
              "category": "factual error"
            },
            {
              "message": "This ADR removes `--scope-files` from the fixer interface, but the existing fixer architecture ADR still defines the fixer port and CLI contract around `scope-files`/`--scope-files`. Without explicitly superseding or revising that ADR, the plan docs now disagree on the intended fixer boundary contract.",
              "severity": "P1",
              "file": "knowledge/adr/2026-06-01-2300-review-fixer-self-resolve-scope-files.md",
              "line": 25,
              "category": "contradiction"
