        {
          "type": "final",
          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "The new guardrail for `track/review.md` is too weak to catch the stale reviewer-model instructions this change is meant to remove. `capabilities.reviewer` is a substring of the old `capabilities.reviewer.model` / `capabilities.reviewer.fast_model` text, and `.harness/config/agent-profiles.json` was already present before this patch, so `verify_override_first_model_resolution` would pass even if review.md still told the orchestrator to resolve and pass `--reviewer-model`. Tighten the required snippet to wording unique to the new self-resolution contract or add the old dotted reviewer-model paths as forbidden snippets.",
