            {
              "message": "This changes the `docker exec` command shape enough to break the repo's workflow snapshot test (`scripts/test_verify_scripts.py::test_ci_uses_host_uid_gid_without_forcing_track_template_dev` still asserts the exact substring `docker exec ci-runner cargo make ci-container`). CI will fail until that test is updated in lockstep.",
